S.FORM: Algeria . Gaga kska Meycow ka Algeria, 28 00 N, 3 00 E ka gaga na nniqan. Kana ka knlbangan na o 2,381,741 sq km (hangan na o Tg10) (knlbanga dxgal o 2,381,741 sq km, knlbangan qsiya o 0 sq km). Kana ka sejiqun o niqan 40,263,711 hiyi. Gaga Algiers ka pusu alang paru, jiyax 1 idas 11 ka jiyax skrayan klwaan. Manu ka dxgal Algeria ga wada sugan 17.30 ka dxgal qpahan, 0.60 ka dxgal bbuyu, rahuq dxgal do niqan 82 na. Bukung klwaan ta sayang o kiya ka Abdelaziz Bouteflika, pnaah hngkawas1999 idas 4 jiyax 27pnrajing kmlawa klwaan.
